dct_title_s:
Africa with the discoveries to May 1858 of Livingstone, Barth, Vogel, & of the
          Chadda expedition, from documents in possession of the Royal Geographical Society
dct_description_sm:
Map based on exploration of Livingstone and Barth. Insets: Cape Verde Islands, Delta of
        the Niger, Cape Colony and Mauritius. Right hand side (top and bottom): 64; Prime meridian
        through Greenwich.
dct_rights_sm: Image from the Dr. Oscar I. Norwich collection of maps of Africa and its islands, 1486 - ca. 1865 courtesy Stanford University Libraries. This item is in the public domain.
